e\u003C/a\u003E for Google's terms. Please also see \u003Ca href=\"https://policies.google.com/privacy?hl=en-GB&gl=uk\"\u003EGoogle's Privacy Policy\u003C/a\u003E. We do not send the API provider any personally identifying information, or information that could uniquely identify your device.\r\n\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003E\r\n\tWhere this notice is displayed in place of a map, agreeing to this notice will store a cookie recording your agreement so you are not prompted again.\r\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp class='wpgmza-centered'\u003E\u003Cbutton class='wpgmza-api-consent'\u003EI agree\u003C/button\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/p\u003E","basic_version":"9.0.22","_isProVersion":"","defaultMarkerIcon":"https://www.cervusbarbershop.ro/wp-content/plugins/wp-google-maps/images/spotlight-poi3.png","markerXMLPathURL":"//www.cervusbarbershop.ro/wp-content/uploads/wp-google-maps/","is_admin":"0","locale":"ro_RO","isServerIIS":"","labelpointIcon":"https://www.cervusbarbershop.ro/wp-content/plugins/wp-google-maps/images/label-point.png","buildCode":"B.9.0.22::A","postID":"661"};
